The paper deals with the problem of corruption detection on networks, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR). The paper also introduces a combinatorial parameter of the graph and uses it to design an efficient algorithm, which falls under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and graph theory (cs.GT). The paper also discusses the computational complexity of the problem, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
